Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.16,0:01:59.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)\blur5}拜托了 让我继续活下去 The Darkest Night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:07.67,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}目を逸らさないで　決めたThe Darkest Night
